        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 3. Ancistrosyllis hamata.A.Whole body, ventral view; firstnotopodial hook on chaetiger 6 (Nh).B.Anterior end, dorsal view,showingpalps.C.Midbodysegmentsshowingnotopodialhooks,dorsalview.D.SEM,detailofanotopodialhookandchaetae, dorsal view. E. Posterior end showing pygidium, ventral view.Abbreviations. Dc:dorsal cirrus, Nh:notopodial hook, Pa: papillae, Pt: prostomium, Pp: palp, Py: pygidium, Pyc: pygidial cirrus. Scale bars: 250 µm (A), 200 µm (B, C), 50 µm (D), 100 µm (E)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4574035/files/figure.png" .

